        <div class='political-about-content'>
          <h2>Meet Adam Azam</h2>
          <div class='political-about-text'>
            <h3>A New Voice for District 11:</h3>
            <p>For over 25 years, our district&#8217;s representation has remained stagnant, while our neighborhoods have faced new and growing challenges.</p>
            <p>Adam Azam is running for State Senate to bring fresh energy, true community empowerment, and a seat at the table for everyone&#8212;not just the well-connected.</p>
            <p>As a community leader and survivor of 9/11, Adam knows that a thriving Queens depends on more than just &quot;business as usual.&quot; He is fighting to turn our diverse community into a political powerhouse. If he can fight for his full rights, he too will fight for yours.</p>
            
            <h3>Our Priorities for Queens:</h3>
            <ul class='volunteer-list'>
              <li>LOCAL LAW 97 threatens affordability of home ownership, forcing co-ops and condos to spend millions in switching from affordable reliable natural gas to costly electrical heating. We must support affordability for ownership in district 11.</li>
              <li>Civic Empowerment: Establishing political learning centers to engage our youth and ensure new voters have a voice in Albany.</li>
              <li>Economic Opportunity: Supporting small businesses and working families through better infrastructure and healthcare access.</li>
              <li>Inclusive Leadership: Bridging the gap for immigrant and multicultural households who have been overlooked for decades.</li>
              <li>Community Resiliency: Investing in sustainable development and neighborhood safety that reflects our values.</li>
            </ul>

            <h3>Invest in the Future of Our District</h3>
            <p>Incremental change is no longer enough.</p>
            <p>We are building a grassroots movement to ensure that District 11 is represented by someone who shares both our daily struggles and our biggest dreams.</p>
            <p>We don&#8217;t have the backing of career politicians and big corporate money, we have something even more valuable, we have you.</p>
            <p>Your contribution helps us fund the canvassing, outreach, and organizing needed to win. Every dollar is a vote for a more inclusive, more resilient, and a more active Queens.</p>
          </div>
          <div class='political-about-image'>
            <img alt='Adam Azam - Candidate for New York State Senate' src='https://github.com/adamazam2749-cmyk/adam-azam-imagess/raw/main/Adam-General-secretary--614x1024.webp'/>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

